{"tid":644352,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：嘉頓餐廳","createTime":"2018-04-27T07:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T17:01:25.000Z","uid":181719,"like":120,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"62479c2237f4485092460ea02268153d88e7799a","tid":644352,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"唔係樓下食雜餅果度，係西餐廳。食TEA冇乜人，檯又隔得疏，好好坐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/153822_0351b77c3a5c60b59e38830abbb11a99.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F153822_0351b77c3a5c60b59e38830abbb11a99.jpeg&h=e57045e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/153843_56628454b0ebb517b7c8bba865d8bb41.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F153843_56628454b0ebb517b7c8bba865d8bb41.jpeg&h=357c13d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢午晚市啲套餐係唔平嘅，都過百一位冇乜走雞，但係TEA就抵食，四五十蚊落到樓。<br />\n<br />\n碟拿破崙雞絲炒意粉呢，嗌之前我係唔知拿破崙汁係咩黎嘅，所以就問咗先，個侍應話唔係茄汁咁頹，就嗌黎試下，結果都係有微微茄汁味，小甜，同幼身意粉超夾。雞絲唔會有太大期望，冇雪味就ok，呢度係好ok嘅，最重要係個意粉好有鑊氣。要喺街食到有鑊氣嘅炒野唔難，但要有鑊氣得黎唔油就超難，呢度算做得幾好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/153915_3437b382001116ceacba66235d90a449.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F153915_3437b382001116ceacba66235d90a449.jpeg&h=c20d277d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相比之下菠菜批係冇咁抵食，只係平幾蚊，但份量好明顯少好多。不過都係絕對值得收貨嘅，因為嗌之前，餐牌話菠菜批係有菠菜有煙肉有蛋有芝士，而我係喺個批度食得返哂呢啲味出黎，口感又夾嘅，就係咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/153938_5cdc65da8548527916aeb477ca05d47f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F153938_5cdc65da8548527916aeb477ca05d47f.jpeg&h=ea6346de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後要讚嘅係杯凍檸茶，茶正常，冰正常，檸檬正常，糖水正常，咁有乜好讚？就係佢平底，易篤檸檬。其實果啲個樣好靚，入面窄底嘅凍飲杯，用黎裝檸類真係難篤到喊出來，好多餐廳都用果款，嘉頓唔係。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/154009_1b181d5bd454754e5882e022ec847a32.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F154009_1b181d5bd454754e5882e022ec847a32.jpeg&h=2b2e8170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n棟野就拆架喇，唔怕比人話我打手，可以讚得盡啲。"},{"pid":"c8446d018e2c1c617786c147e540ec8f74582020","tid":644352,"uid":60089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:47:51.000Z","msg":"細細個成日係呢度既前身食野, 即係嘉頓酒樓飲茶"},{"pid":"e97ba1e20c8504587bfcbd3f29b0938305e2c98b","tid":644352,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c8446d018e2c1c617786c147e540ec8f74582020","tid":644352,"uid":60089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:47:51.000Z","msg":"細細個成日係呢度既前身食野, 即係嘉頓酒樓飲茶"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:01:19.000Z","msg":"以前係點架？巴打講多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b7af2a9a06fca731e21fe1a49345cede20f553","tid":644352,"uid":42734,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:14:30.000Z","msg":"下次試吓，剩係喺樓下食過餅"},{"pid":"42da123449cd8944f18d90e70467de115387139e","tid":644352,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6b7af2a9a06fca731e21fe1a49345cede20f553","tid":644352,"uid":42734,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:14:30.000Z","msg":"下次試吓，剩係喺樓下食過餅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:23:34.000Z","msg":"樓下啲餅個樣就真係唔太吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a2b436df4b1da0002a9637cf409080ce03c189","tid":644352,"uid":60089,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e97ba1e20c8504587bfcbd3f29b0938305e2c98b","tid":644352,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c8446d018e2c1c617786c147e540ec8f74582020","tid":644352,"uid":60089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:47:5